          <h1 class="doc-heading">RunPod GraphQL API Spec</h1>
          <div id="introduction" data-traverse-target="introduction">
            <div id="welcome" class="doc-row">
              <div class="doc-copy">
                <p>RunPod API spec includes most common GraphQL types, queries, and mutations to manage your pods. If you need additional support, <a href="https://contact.runpod.io">contact us</a>.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="doc-examples">
                <div class="example-section welcome-api-endpoints-section example-section-is-code">
                  <h5>API Endpoints</h5>
                  <pre><code>https://api.runpod.io/graphql</code></pre>
                </div>
                <div class="example-section welcome-api-endpoints-section example-section-is-code">
                  <h5>Headers</h5>
                  <pre><code>Authorization: Bearer &lt;RUNPOD_API_KEY&gt;</code></pre>
                </div>
                <div class="example-section welcome-version-section">
                  <h5>Version</h5>
                  <p>1.1.0</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h1 id="group-Operations-Queries" class="group-heading" data-traverse-target="group-Operations-Queries">Queries</h1>
          <section id="query-cpuTypes" class="operation operation-query" data-traverse-target="query-cpuTypes">
            <h2 class="operation-heading ">
              <code>cpuTypes</code>
            </h2>
            <div class="doc-row">
              <div class="doc-copy">
                <div class="operation-response doc-copy-section">
                  <h5>Response</h5>
                  <p> Returns <a href="#definition-CpuType"><code>[CpuType]</code></a>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="doc-examples">
                <h4 class="example-heading">Example</h4>
                <div class="example-section example-section-is-code operation-query-example">
                  <h5>Query</h5>
                  <pre><code class="hljs language-gql"><span class="hljs-symbol"><span class="hljs-keyword">query</span> cpuTypes <span class="hljs-tag">{
  <span class="hljs-symbol">cpuTypes <span class="hljs-tag">{
    <span class="hljs-symbol">id</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">displayName</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">manufacturer</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">cores</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">threadsPerCore</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">groupId</span>
  }</span></span>
}</span></span>
</code></pre>
                </div>
                <div class="example-section example-section-is-code operation-response-example">
                  <h5>Response</h5>
                  <pre><code class="hljs language-json"><span class="hljs-punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">"data"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">{</span>
    <span class="hljs-attr">"cpuTypes"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span>
      <span class="hljs-punctuation">{</span>
        <span class="hljs-attr">"id"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">"xyz789"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span>
        <span class="hljs-attr">"displayName"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">"abc123"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span>
        <span class="hljs-attr">"manufacturer"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">"abc123"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span>
        <span class="hljs-attr">"cores"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">987</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span>
        <span class="hljs-attr">"threadsPerCore"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">987</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span>
        <span class="hljs-attr">"groupId"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">"abc123"</span>
      <span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span>
    <span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span>
  <span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span>
<span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          <section id="query-gpuTypes" class="operation operation-query" data-traverse-target="query-gpuTypes">

                    <thead>
                      <tr>
                        <th>Name</th>
                        <th>Description</th>
                      </tr>
                    </thead>

                  <h5>Query</h5>
                  <pre><code class="hljs language-gql"><span class="hljs-symbol"><span class="hljs-keyword">query</span> gpuTypes<span class="hljs-tag">(<span class="hljs-code">$input</span>:<span class="hljs-type"> GpuTypeFilter)</span> {
  gpuTypes(input: <span class="hljs-code">$input</span>)</span> <span class="hljs-tag">{
    <span class="hljs-symbol">lowestPrice <span class="hljs-tag">{
      <span class="hljs-type">...LowestPriceFragment</span>
    }</span></span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">maxGpuCount</span>

    <span class="hljs-symbol">nodeGroupDatacenters <span class="hljs-tag">{

    }</span></span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">id</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">displayName</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">manufacturer</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">memoryInGb</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">cudaCores</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">secureCloud</span>

    <span class="hljs-symbol">securePrice</span>

    <span class="hljs-symbol">oneWeekPrice</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">communitySpotPrice</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">secureSpotPrice</span>
    <span class="hljs-symbol">throughput</span>
  }</span></span>
}
</code></pre>
                </div>

</code></pre>
                </div>
                <div class="example-section example-section-is-code operation-response-example">
                  <h5>Response</h5>
                  <pre><code class="hljs language-json"><span class="hljs-punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">"data"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">{</span>
    <span class="hljs-attr">"gpuTypes"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span>
      <span class="hljs-punctuation">{</span>
